AVR base libraray
Copyright (C) 2013-2021 Tohid Jafarzadeh <tohid.jk@gmail.com>
License GNU GPLv2

This is simple and low level library for work with hardware registers.
All writen by gnu c preproccesor.
For arv-gcc compiler used in ATMEL Studio, WinAVR, Arduino.
Support atmega32,16,8 mcu.

Report bugs to <tohid.jk@gmail.com>.

